{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_080.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x16,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "This ruin is totally empty now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "They're here and there, but you have lots of ruins all around this area."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "At one time, back when my dad was still active, I heard it used to be livelier with more people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "But by the time I was old enough to know what was going on, it was basically already like this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hearing that, I can almost sense the history in this place. What were people able to gather here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Stone materials. Well, it's<CR>weather-beaten around here,<CR>so the quality isn't that good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I guess it used to be a hard place to work. You know how there are towers?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "The ground was loose because it was marshland, and many of them collapsed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...There was an accident during an excavation here, and that's why my dad had to retire."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Thinking back, this isn't my favorite place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see... I'm sorry, I was so insensitive."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh no, don't feel sad.<CR>It wasn't life-threatening."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "He's tougher than the guys around here, and he's still healthy, working in the fields."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It's just that with his injury he<CR>couldn't do heavy physical labor,<CR>so he retired from being a prospector."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "\"Then, I'll succeed my dad!\"<CR>...That's how I started doing this job, but.."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I was too hasty. Thinking back, there was no reason for me to do the same job..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but I think being a prospector suits you, Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, I actually think so, too. Digging for buried treasures ain't bad."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But, I do wonder how long I'll be able to keep doing this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "(How long you can keep doing something... I've never thought about such a thing.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "(But, I feel like that's really important...)"
        }
    ]
}